OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother fine start and soon
OL,6,Ffeeling very warm in the sunshine.
OL,7,FCloudier conditions developing through
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, with perhaps some rain
OL,9,For showers making gradual inroads from
OL,10,Fthe west later, perhaps culminating in
OL,11,Fsome thundery showers locally.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny rain or thundery showers
OL,14,Fwill soon clear eastwards, leaving a
OL,15,Fmostly dry night. Variable cloud
OL,16,Fovernight and mild, with a few mist or
OL,17,Ffog patches possible by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
