OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FVariable cloud and sunny
OL,6,Fspells are expected on Saturday.
OL,7,FIsolated showers are possible during
OL,8,Fthe day, but many places dry, with
OL,9,Frain or thundery showers perhaps
OL,10,Fdeveloping more widely later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMore
OL,13,Funsettled than recently, with rain or
OL,14,Fshowers, some thundery. Gradually
OL,15,Fturning cooler. More sunny spells from
OL,16,FMonday, but still also showers, these
OL,17,Fbecoming lighter and further between
OL,18,Fon Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
